data.description: Refined living in this captivating residence in Vero Beach's prestigious Millstone South community. Perfectly positioned on a spacious corner lot, this home offers tranquility with its serene pond views. The main level unfolds with an expansive open floor design, leading to 4 generously sized bedrooms upstairs. Fresh with new carpeting & paint, this home is pristine and move-in ready. Millstone South boasts a welcoming clubhouse, fitness center, shimmering lake, pool, tennis & pickleball courts all connected by lush sidewalks perfect for peaceful strolls. Vero Beach's allure extends beyond the community. Known as a coastal paradise, the nearby Atlantic Ocean invites you to enjoy fishing, boating, diving, and more. The Indian River Lagoon offers a haven for kayaking and paddleboarding
